Check out 48 lbs of nasty.

00:16.884 --> 00:18.384
Both: No!

00:18.386 --> 00:22.454
Well!
( chuckles )

00:22.456 --> 00:26.558
Looky here.
The male... Physique.

00:26.560 --> 00:28.927
Why thank you, art lady.

00:28.929 --> 00:30.929
Why aren't
we drawing lucas?

00:33.500 --> 00:35.467
