straight to the gun show.

00:51.384 --> 00:54.319
Maya, you're supposed
to concentrate on the eyes.

00:54.321 --> 00:56.455
See, you know
what my problem is?
I don't listen.

00:56.457 --> 00:58.223
By the way,
you're drawing lucas.

00:59.325 --> 01:01.026
Oh.
( chuckles )

01:01.995 --> 01:04.263
Well, that's the first time

01:04.265 --> 01:05.531
I've ever done that.

01:10.837 --> 01:12.004
Do I need help?

01:13.473 --> 01:15.574
All right, I know these
are works in progress,

01:15.576 --> 01:16.909
But let's see
where we are.

01:16.911 --> 01:19.278
Maybe we'll become
famous artists.

01:19.280 --> 01:20.979
We'll go to paris,

01:20.981 --> 01:24.249
Drink coffee
in outdoor cafes.

01:24.251 --> 01:25.617
How do I look?

01:25.619 --> 01:28.687
( vocalizing tune )

01:34.894 --> 01:37.329
( humphs )

01:37.331 --> 01:38.997
Fine, make fun of me.

01:38.999 --> 01:42.568
I am a serious artist
who belongs in paris.

01:42.570 --> 01:44.570
<i>Bonjour, </i> lucas.

01:44.572 --> 01:46.638
( speaking
french )

01:54.647 --> 01:56.582
<i>Bonjour, </i> lucas.

01:59.385 --> 02:01.753
- Oh my gosh.
- See?  I am an artist.

02:01.755 --> 02:04.690
- I am finally something.
- Maya.

02:04.692 --> 02:06.925
( annoyed )
what a life I'm having.

02:06.927 --> 02:09.695
Maya.  My goodness.

02:09.697 --> 02:13.699
This is brilliant!

02:13.701 --> 02:16.401
Farkle is
in a bird's nest.

02:16.403 --> 02:18.737
It's a work
of surrealism, riley.

02:18.739 --> 02:21.707
It's how this artist's mind
views the subject.

02:21.709 --> 02:23.609
I'm a bird to you?

02:23.611 --> 02:26.645
No, you just...
Need to be protected.

02:26.647 --> 02:28.847
- You love me.
- Leave me alone.

02:30.016 --> 02:31.950
Maya, there's a school
exhibit coming up.

02:31.952 --> 02:33.619
I want one
of your pieces in it.

02:33.621 --> 02:35.721
What about my piece?
( chuckles )

02:36.990 --> 02:39.057
That's a cute top.

02:40.527 --> 02:42.094
No thanks, miss kossal.

02:42.096 --> 02:44.863
I don't draw for other people
to look at, but thank you.

02:44.865 --> 02:47.032
I'd appreciate you
thinking about it, okay?

02:51.004 --> 02:53.672
- Where you headed, farkle?
- Gym class.

02:53.674 --> 02:55.073
That should go well, right?

02:55.075 --> 02:58.243
<i>( theme music playing )</i>

03:02.115 --> 03:04.116
<i>♪ I've been waiting</i>

03:04.118 --> 03:05.617
